%div{style: 'position:absolute; top:5px; right:5px', id: 'share_privacy_policy'}
  - email_body = "Dear parents,\n\nSoftware and technology are everywhere - in our computers, in our pockets, in our cars, and used in banking, communications, entertainment, transportation, and science, to name a few. However, very few kids are learning how to actually create technology. In today’s world, computer science is fundamental for preparing students to be informed and successful in our increasingly technological society, regardless of what career path their future holds.\n\nThis year we’re proud to be teaching computer science in our classroom using Code.org’s online learning platform and curriculum. Code.org takes student privacy very seriously and has earned one of the highest privacy ratings from Common Sense Media.  You can read their privacy notice here: https://code.org/privacy/student-privacy\n\nI’d encourage you to ask your student about what they are learning and have them show you the programs or games they create this year!\n\nThanks,"
  %label
    Share this notice with parents:
  %a{class:'share-on-remind', href:'https://www.remind.com/v1/share?url=code.org/privacy/student-privacy&referer=code.org&text=Code.org%20Student%20Privacy%20Policy', target:'_blank', id: 'share_on_remind'}
  %a{class: 'email-button', href: "mailto:?to=&body=" + CGI.escape(email_body), target:'_blank', id: 'email_button'}
    %i.fa.fa-envelope{"aria-hidden": "true"}
    Email
  %a{class: 'print-button', href: "javascript:window.print()", id: 'print_button'}
    %i.fa.fa-print{"aria-hidden": "true"}
    Print

%script{src: minifiable_asset_path("js/code.org/views/share_privacy.js")}

%body
  :css
    .share-on-remind {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 185px;
      height: 40px;
      background: url("/images/share-on-remind-button-with-text.png") no-repeat top;
      background-position: center top;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .share-on-remind:active {
      background-position: center bottom;
    }
    .email-button, .print-button {
      background-color: #7665a0;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      width: 90px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 40px;
      vertical-align: middle;
    }
    .email-button:visited, .print-button:visited, .email-button:link, .print-button:link {
        color: white;
    }
    @media print {
      #share_privacy_policy {
        display: none
      }
    }
